**Much at Stake for Tech Sector in UID Project** is a news report published by *The Times of India* on 12 December 2011, written by Pranav Nambiar. The article examines the potential impact on India's technology sector following uncertainty around the Unique Identification (UID or Aadhaar) project after objections raised by a Parliamentary Standing Committee. The article was also published on [*The Economic Times*](/media/much-at-stake-tech-sector-uid-project) on the same date.

